 of Canada]] || [[Classic (transit bus)|GMC Classic]] || 40 || 47-49 || [[Diesel Engine|Diesel]] || [[Detroit Diesel Series 71|Detroit Diesel 6V-71N]] || 1900-1999 || 100 || 2002\n|-\n|1989|| [[Motor Coach Industries]] || [[Classic (transit bus)|MCI Classic]] || 40 || 51 || [[Diesel Engine|Diesel]] || [[Detroit Diesel Series 71|Detroit Diesel 8V-92TA]] || 2000-2084 || 85 || 2003\n|-\n|1989|| [[Neoplan USA]] || AN460 || 60 || 65 || [[Diesel Engine|Diesel]] || [[Detroit Diesel Series 92|Detroit Diesel 6V-92TA]] || 8900-8913 || 14 || 2002\n|-\n|1992|| [[New Flyer]] || D40HF || 40 || 45 || [[Diesel Engine|Diesel]] || [[Detroit Diesel Series 92|Detroit Diesel 8V-92]] || 3000-3120 || 121 || 2005\n|-\n|1995|| [[Nova Bus]] || [[Rapid Transit Series|RTS 06]] || 40 || 43 || [[Diesel Engine|Diesel]] ||  [[Detroit Diesel Series 50]] || 3200-3232 || 33 || 2008\n|-\n|1996|| [[Goshen Coach]] || MB19FD || 30|| 19 || [[Diesel Engine|Diesel]] || [[Cummins B Series engine|Cummins 5.9L B-Series]] || 3300-3328 || 29 || 2001\n|-\n|1996|| [[Nova Bus]] || [[Rapid Transit Series|RTS 06]] || 40 || 43 || [[Diesel Engine|Diesel]] ||  [[Detroit Diesel Series 50]] || 3500-3599 || 100 || 2012\n|-\n|1997|| [[Nova Bus]] || [[Rapid Transit Series|RTS 06]] || 40 || 43 || [[Diesel Engine|Diesel]] ||  [[Detroit Diesel Series 50]] || 3250-3282 || 33 || 2012\n|-\n|1997|| [[Nova Bus]] || [[Rapid Transit Series|RTS 06]] || 40 || 43 || [[Diesel Engine|Diesel]] ||  [[Detroit Diesel Series 50]] || 3600-3617 || 18 || 2012\n|-\n|1997|| [[Nova Bus]] || [[Rapid Transit Series|RTS 06]] || 40 || 39 || [[Diesel Engine|Diesel]] ||  [[Detroit Diesel Series 50]] || 3290-3299 || 10 || 2010\n|-\n|1998|| [[Optima Bus Corporation|Chance Bus Corp]] || CNG-28 || 28 || 27 || [[Natural gas vehicle|CNG]] ||  [[Cummins B Series engine|Cummins 5.9L B-Series]] || 4000-4003 || 4 || 2004\n|-\n|1998|| [[Optima Bus Corporation|Chance Bus Corp]] || CNG-28 || 28 || 27 || [[Natural gas vehicle|CNG]] ||  [[Cummins B Series engine|Cummins 