ell/Southfield\n* Fenkell/Schaefer\n* Fenkell/Dexter\n* 14th/Oakman\n* 14th/W. Grand Blvd.\n* 14th/Grand River\n* 14th/Fisher\n* Rosa Parks Transit Center\n || \n* Rosa Parks Transit Center \n* Rosa Parks/Fisher\n* Rosa Parks/Grand River\n* Rosa Parks/W. Grand Blvd.\n* Rossa Parks/Oakman\n* Fenkell/Dexter\n* Fenkell/Schaefer\n* Fenkell/Southfield\n* Fenkell/Dale\n||\n* [https://detroitmi.gov/document/18-fenkell 18 Fenkell Schedule]\n|-\n| 19 Fort || \n* Fort/W. Outer Drive\n* Fort/Scahefer\n* Fort/Livernois\n* Fort/Clark\n* Fort/Rosa Parks\n* Rosa Parks Transit Center\n|| \n* Rosa Parks Transit Center\n* Fort/Rosa Parks\n* Fort/Clark\n* Fort/Livernois\n* Fort/Schaefer\n* Fort/W. Outer Dr.\n || \n* [https://detroitmi.gov/document/19-fort 19 Fort Schedule]\n|-\n| 23 Hamilton || \n* Meijer Gateway\n* John R/7 Mile\n* Hamilton/McNichols\n* M-10 (Lodge Fwy)/Clairmount\n* 3rd/W. Grand Blvd.\n* Anthony Wayne/Warren\n* Rosa Parks Transit Center \n||\n* Rosa Parks Transit Center\n* Anthony Wayne/Warren\n* 2nd/Grand Blvd.\n* M-10 (Lodge Fwy)/Clairmount\n* Hamilton/McNichols\n* John R/7 Mile\n* Meijer Gateway\n|| \n* [https://detroitmi.gov/document/23-hamilton 23 Hamilton Schedule]\n|-\n| 27 Joy || \n* Redford Plaza\n* Joy/Spinoza\n* Joy/Greenfield\n* Joy/Schaefer\n* Joy/Livernois\n* Tireman/Beechwood\n* Grand River/Grand Blvd.\n* Grand Blvd./Michigan\n* Lafayette/Trumbull\n* Rosa Parks Transit Center\n|| \n* Rosa Parks Transit Center\n* Lafayette/Trumbull\n* Grand Blvd./Michigan\n* Grand River/Grand Blvd.\n* Tireman/Beechwood\n* Joy/Livernois\n* Joy/Schaefer\n* Joy/Greenfield\n* Joy/Spinoza\n* Redford Plaza\n||\n* [https://detroitmi.gov/document/27-joy 27 Joy Schedule]\n|-\n| 29 Linwood || \n* Livernois/Florence\n* Linwood/Fenkell\n* Linwood/W. Grand Blvd\n* Trumbull/Warren\n* Trumbull/Michigan\n* Rosa Parks Transit Center \n||\n* Rosa Parks Transit Center\n* Trumbull/Michigan\n* Trumbull/Warren\n* Linwood/W. Grand Blvd.\n* Linwood/Fenkell\n* Livernois/Florence\n ||\n* [https